text: Rustlers' Rhapsody is a 1985 American western comedy movie directed by Hugh Wilson. It stars Tom Berenger, G.W. Bailey, Marilu Henner, Andy Griffin, Fernando Rey, Sela Ward, Patrick Wayne, Jim Carter, Paul Maxwell and Christopher Malcolm. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures and was a box office failure. ==Other websites== * Category:1985 comedy movies Category:1980s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Paramount Pictures movies
